Cook*MTF*Paul*John,hi,it's me psycho Dan Knight,can say this we who went to Nam can be seen,it's a great day I ain't out driving on the road having a seizure killing anyone.I too am worried about Iraq and our response as a country to the Psychotic leader they have.I have this view just like Vietnam,the rich gain wealth and the poor loose family members.I heard on c-span that the Gulf War cost our country  not one dime.this pisses me off,where do these brainless reporters get their information??Who in the hell do they think is paying for all of the residules of that war,and it is still not over,what about these soldiers who are making believe they suffer from Gulf War Syndrome&quot;So damn well they are even Dying&quot;do these idiot reporters believe this money comes from another demension.I live very close to Ft.Hood and they have been extremely active,tanks,artillary&quot;ALL NIGHT&quot;&quot;ALL DAY&quot;and even on the small arms ranges.Also there are many transports,rail flat cars,c-5A's.It's getting scary,they do not care about anything but making money and they will do anything for it.I guess I should say thanks to the guy who came back from Canada,since I am a 100%totally disabled Veteran an did get a 2.5%chairty increase,THANK YOU SIR!!!As for the President,I personally do not like being lied to,he and the congress/senate&quot;both sides&quot;are guilty and I would prefer seeing the President getting screwed instead of me,I am sure I speak for my wife also in this reguard.For YOU my Friends out there please think about this,What does it take to engauge in war?Answer:MONEY Where does it come from?Answer:US,OK;Be Honnest&quot;Do WE FEEL A LITTLE SCREWED?&quot;NOW;Where Does It GO&quot;?TO THE WEALTHY,they are the ones who make the essentials,OIL-GAS-OTHER FUEL'S,AIRCRAFT,FOOD,WATER,TRANSPORTATION,TENTS,WEAPONS,AMMUNITIONS,CHEMICALS,MEDICATIONS,***INSURENCE**&amp;AGENTS**,TOBACCO,MOTORS,LIGHTBULBS,THREAD,CLOTHING,LUMBER,STEEL,COMPUTERS,PROGRAMMING,MATCHES,LIGHTERS,STAMPS,Lets not forget that where ever we load/unload cargo we pay import/export taxes,COMMUNICATIONS,PERSONAL COMMUNICATIONS ande the TAXES on the calls made home to MOM&amp;Dad&amp;Wives&amp;Friends,INNOCCULATIONS and the HAZZARDS THEY REPRESENT,Fines for running over SADDAM'S CHICKENS&lt;GOATS&lt;PALACES,SNACKS,BEVERAGES,I think you all get a little bit of the picture.Hey There Canada,You I pray will ask the rest of the guy's still over there to come back home,With my swimming pool I will need another 2.5% chairty raise next year for sure,that is if they ever get the plaster applied.This old Outlaw-11 Vietnam Veteran 1964-1973 will catch you great people latter.going arrowhead hunting,Take Care,CRAZY YES,STUPID NO WAY******************
